AVX-512 features (I): More & Bigger 
Registers
AVX: VADDPS YMM0, YMM3, [mem]
 Up to 16 AVX registers
 8 in 32-bit mode
 256-bit width
 8 x FP32
 4 x FP64
AVX-512: VADDPS ZMM0, ZMM24, [mem]
 Up to 32 AVX registers
 8 in 32-bit mode
 512-bit width
 16 x FP32
 8 x FP64
But you need many more features
to use all that real estate effectively…
